title: The Devil Wears Prada Discography 2005-2013 (15 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
THE DEVIL WEARS PRADA DISCOGRAPHY DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 15 releases...

 * 2005 - Patterns Of A Horizon
 * 2006 - Dear Love A Beautiful Discord
 * 2007 - Plagues
 * 2007 - Spongebob Grindpants - Single
 * 2008 - Html Rulez D00d - Demo
 * 2008 - Still Fly - Single
 * 2009 - With Roots Above And Branches Below
 * 2011 - Born To Lose - Single
 * 2011 - Dead Throne
 * 2011 - Dead Throne - Instrumental
 * 2011 - Zombie EP
 * 2012 - Dead And Alive
 * 2013 - 8-18
 * 2013 - 8-18 - Japanese Edition
 * 2013 - Martyrs - Home For Grave - Single

The Devil Wears Prada was founded during 2005 in Dayton Ohio; they derived their band name from the story with the same title. Being founded with all Christian members and maintaining a theme that represents their religion, the group played their first show in 2005 with a fill-in bassist and only one guitarist. Rhythm guitarist Jeremy Depoyster and bassist Andy Trick joined the band soon afterward. They continued playing at local areas in Dayton before recording their demo later in the year which was titled Patterns of a Horizon.

In Christ,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
